---
// packages/web/src/components/chains/HowItWorks.astro
//
// Explains how users interact with Drivechains through Sidecoin.
// Key message: the app abstracts chain complexity.
---

<section class="border-t border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/30">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20">

    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl">
      How It <span class="text-amber-400">Works</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-center text-gray-400">
      Sidecoin handles the complexity so you don't have to.
    </p>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-950 p-6 text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-amber-800/40 bg-amber-950/30 font-mono text-lg font-bold text-amber-400">
          1
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-5 text-base font-semibold text-white">
          One Unified Platform
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          You interact with Sidecoin as a single wallet.
          No manual chain switching, no separate apps,
          no complex configuration.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="relative rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-950 p-6 text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-amber-800/40 bg-amber-950/30 font-mono text-lg font-bold text-amber-400">
          2
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-5 text-base font-semibold text-white">
          Chains Operate Behind the Scenes
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          When you make a payment, swap an asset, or use a
          smart contract, Sidecoin routes your action to the
          appropriate sidechain automatically.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="relative rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-950 p-6 text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-amber-800/40 bg-amber-950/30 font-mono text-lg font-bold text-amber-400">
          3
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-5 text-base font-semibold text-white">
          Seamless Fund Movement
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Funds move between chains through BIP-300 deposits
          and withdrawals. Sidecoin manages these transfers
          so your assets are always where they need to be.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Technical footnote -->
    <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-950 p-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
        <span class="font-semibold text-gray-400">Under the hood:</span>
        BIP-300 Hashrate Escrows manage sidechain deposits and withdrawals
        with a ~6 month withdrawal window (26,300 blocks). BIP-301 Blind
        Merged Mining allows Bitcoin miners to secure all sidechains
        simultaneously without running additional node software.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
